org.mozilla.geckoview

Interface MediaElement.Delegate

  • Enclosing class:
    MediaElement

    public static interface MediaElement.Delegate
    This interface allows apps to handle media events.

        time - The current playback time in seconds.

      • onPlaybackRateChange
